parameter 40: The original German version of C&C: Generals, already slightly cut, was rated FSK 16 (16 years and above) but was banned mainly due because of the Terrorists-faction. EA then released a new heavily edited version called Command&Conquer: Generäle. The main changes in this version were the cut of one GLA mission where the player has to attack UN-convoys and also kill civilians and the suicide-bomber unit was removed and replaced by some kind of RC-vehicle with a bomb attached to it.
